item.title: New partners for July 12th
item.description: Since Nexus Food Delivery is still in the works, we’re currently in the process of acquiring partners. After all, without having partners, we won’t have any food to deliver! Well, we’ve been hard at work on that, and we’re proud today to announce the arrival of 4 new partners. These restaurants have decided to partner up with Nexus Food Delivery and allow us to deliver their food to you, the fine people of Cookeville, TN.
